STATE
v.
Gabriel A. FERRARI 277P18-4 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019

Gabriel Adrian Ferrari, Talbott, For Gabriel A. Ferrari

Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of North Carolina

Todd Williams, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of April 2019 by Defendant to Strike the Court Order to Dismiss as Illegal and Non Constitutional in Violation of Defendant's Constitutional Rights, TN Law and U.S. Federal Rules, by Court in Conference on March 27, 2019:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
